{"tid":90492,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[無圖]新年最唔想收到咩拜年賀禮？","createTime":"2017-01-22T06:40:58.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T13:41:05.000Z","uid":3933,"like":2,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8fb98c703b1ccb21f9596e273a2aef15e32a385e","tid":90492,"uid":3933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:40:58.000Z","msg":"1. 蛋卷<br />\n唔好食之餘又容易食到周圍都係<br />\n包裝又老土見到都唔開胃<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmNfEJGsFoAE8xjuaAGtrZKGgUMCjnNqEHtHBn77nX5M3m?filename=cM1hSV7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcM1hSV7.jpg&h=e65bbd3a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. 鮑魚麵<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/22/143307_d3035df0a19aa74c71011cdc70e2de55.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F22%2F143307_d3035df0a19aa74c71011cdc70e2de55.jpg&h=8bf30597&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n3.幾十蚊一盒既雜牌曲奇/朱古力<br />\n收到應該檢討下自己平時點對人<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmaVcDU3o9iNNkFG3aHnBUR7K2KhXp49w4hoqazS8fPoJS?filename=bC0p54Y.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbC0p54Y.jpg&h=652f5681&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n4.瑞士糖<br />\n唔明點解會有人買瑞士糖送禮 仲要驚死你唔夠食大大罐 慘撚過收嘉頓雜餅<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWh3TL77dsPA136yN8rXbzxoUKeShBpb1u512VgosxWKR?filename=h9e4kK2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh9e4kK2.jpg&h=f0bcd7db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n暫時諗到咁多<br />\n拆開見到會覺得好掃興<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"233eda96cdbe4cd8c2ee1e2d47929801fdc1c33e","tid":90492,"uid":3381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:41:43.000Z","msg":"嘉頓"},{"pid":"c2cc244e8954ef1ed079df3248140f75f79a3f10","tid":90492,"uid":23330,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:43:02.000Z","msg":"鮑魚麵先好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/win